.8, "end": 34.48, "text": "My uncle owns a big farm.", "words": [{"w": "My", "s": 31.8, "e": 32.64}, {"w": "uncle", "s": 32.64, "e": 32.96}, {"w": "owns", "s": 32.96, "e": 33.5}, {"w": "a", "s": 33.5, "e": 33.7}, {"w": "big", "s": 33.7, "e": 33.94}, {"w": "farm.", "s": 33.94, "e": 34.48}]}, {"start": 37.62, "end": 41.36, "text": "Many people notice the importance of agriculture in Japan.", "words": [{"w": "Many", "s": 37.62, "e": 38.12}, {"w": "people", "s": 38.12, "e": 38.54}, {"w": "notice", "s": 38.54, "e": 38.96}, {"w": "the", "s": 38.96, "e": 39.28}, {"w": "importance", "s": 39.28, "e": 39.68}, {"w": "of", "s": 39.68, "e": 40.0}, {"w": "agriculture", "s": 40.0, "e": 40.48}, {"w": "in", "s": 40.48, "e": 40.9}, {"w": "Japan.", "s": 40.9, "e": 41.36}]}, {"start": 44.2, "end": 50.16, "text": "It is not physically possible for a human to run 100 meters in 8 seconds.", "words": [{"w": "It", "s": 44.2, "e": 45.04}, {"w": "is", "s": 45.04, "e": 45.22}, {"w": "not", "s": 45.22, "e": 45.46}, {"w": "physically", "s": 45.46, "e": 45.86}, {"w": "possible", "s": 45.86, "e": 46.52}, {"w": "for", "s": 46.52, "e": 46.92}, {"w": "a", "s": 46.92, "e": 47.08}, {"w": "human", "s": 47.08, "e": 47.36}, {"w": "to", "s": 47.36, "e": 47.68}, {"w": "run", "s": 47.68, "e": 47.96}, {"w": "100", "s": 47.96, "e": 48.52}, {"w": "meters", "s": 48.52, "e": 48.82}, {"w": "in", "s": 48.82, "e": 49.38}, {"w": "8", "s": 49.38, "e": 49.68}, {"w": "seconds.", "s": 49.68, "e": 50.16}]}, {"start": 53.14, "end": 57.18, "text": "I had a bad cold and therefore could not go to school.", "words": [{"w": "I", "s": 53.14, "e": 53.8}, {"w": "had", "s": 53.8, "e": 54.04}, {"w": "a", "s": 54.04, "e": 54.16}, {"w": "bad", "s": 54.16, "e": 54.4}, {"w": "cold", "s": 54.4, "e": 54.88}, {"w": "and", "s": 54.88, "e": 55.4}, {"w": "therefore", "s": 55.4, "e": 55.84}, {"w": "could", "s": 55.84, "e": 56.18}, {"w": "not", "s": 56.18, "e": 56.42}, {"w": "go", "s": 56.42, "e": 56.66}, {"w": "to", "s": 56.66, "e": 56.82}, {"w": "school.", "s": 56.82, "e": 57.18}]}, {"start": 60.12, "end": 64.26, "text": "We lost the game and thus won't be able to go to the finals.", "words": [{"w": "We", "s": 60.12, "e": 60.78}, {"w": "lost", "s": 60.78, "e": 61.18}, {"w": "the", "s": 61.18, "e": 61.4}, {"w": "game", "s": 61.4, "e": 61.72}, {"w": "and", "s": 61.72, "e": 62.06}, {"w": "thus", "s": 62.06, "e": 62.34}, {"w": "won't", "s": 62.34, "e": 62.76}, {"w": "be", "s": 62.76, "e": 62.96}, {"w": "able", "s": 62.96, "e": 63.18}, {"w": "to", "s": 63.18, "e": 63.4}, {"w": "go", "s": 63.4, "e": 63.58}, {"w": "to", "s": 63.58, "e": 63.74}, {"w": "the", "s": 63.74, "e": 63.88}, {"w": "finals.", "s": 63.88, "e": 64.26}]}, {"start": 67.42, "end": 71.66, "text": "We'd better take a map, otherwise we might get lost.", "words": [{"w": "We'd", "s": 67.42, "e": 68.08}, {"w": "better", "s": 68.08, "e": 68.34}, {"w": "take", "s": 68.34, "e": 68.62}, {"w": "a", "s": 68.62, "e": 68.8}, {"w": "map,", "s": 68.8, "e": 69.14}, {"w": "otherwise", "s": 69.6, "e": 70.1}, {"w": "we", "s": 70.1, "e": 70.66}, {"w": "might", "s": 70.66, "e": 70.9}, {"w": "get", "s": 70.9, "e": 71.14}, {"w": "lost.", "s": 71.14, "e": 71.66}]}, {"start": 74.52, "end": 78.06, "text": "Finish this exercise before the end of class.", "words": [{"w": "Finish", "s": 74.52, "e": 75.28}, {"w": "this", "s": 75.28, "e": 75.62}, {"w": "exercise", "s": 75.62, "e": 76.32}, {"w": "before", "s": 76.32, "e": 76.82}, {"w": "the", "s": 76.82, "e": 77.16}, {"w": "end", "s": 77.16, "e": 77.4}, {"w": "of", "s": 77.4, "e": 77.52}, {"w": "class.", "s": 77.52, "e": 78.06}]}, {"start": 81.14, "end": 82.98, "text": "Practice makes perfect.", "words": [{"w": "Practice", "s": 81.14, "e": 81.9}, {"w": "makes", "s": 81.9, "e": 82.4}, {"w": "perfect.", "s": 82.4, "e": 82.98}]}, {"start": 85.84, "end": 88.64, "text": "I don't think the invention is practical.", "words": [{"w": "I", "s": 85.84, "e": 86.6}, {"w": "don't", "s": 86.6, "e": 86.86}, {"w": "think", "s": 86.86, "e": 87.12}, {"w": "the", "s": 87.12, "e": 87.32}, {"w": "invention", "s": 87.32, "e": 87.8}, {"w": "is", "s": 87.8, "e": 88.12}, {"w": "practical.", "s": 88.12, "e": 88.64}]}, {"start": 91.68, "end": 96.26, "text": "Your plans are good in theory, but they won't work in practice.", "words": [{"w": "Your", "s": 91.68, "e": 92.38}, {"w": "plans", "s": 92.38, "e": 92.82}, {"w": "are", "s": 92.82, "e": 93.1}, {"w": "good", "s": 93.1, "e": 93.42}, {"w": "in", "s": 93.42, "e": 93.7}, {"w": "theory,", "s": 93.7, "e": 94.08}, {"w": "but", "s": 94.44, "e": 94.7}, {"w": "they", "s": 94.7, "e": 94.94}, {"w": "won't", "s": 94.94, "e": 95.32}, {"w": "work", "s": 95.32, "e": 95.66}, {"w": "in", "s": 95.66, "e": 95.86}, {"w": "practice.", "s": 95.86, "e": 96.26}]}, {"start": 99.28, "end": 103.0, "text": "It was cold and in addition, it was windy.", "words": [{"w": "It", "s": 99.28, "e": 100.0}, {"w": "was", "s": 100.0, "e": 100.22}, {"w": "cold", "s": 100.22, "e": 100.64}, {"w": "and", "s": 100.64, "e": 101.26}, {"w": "in", "s": 101.26, "e": 101.46}, {"w": "addition,", "s": 101.46, "e": 101.82}, {"w": "it", "s": 102.24, "e": 102.4}, {"w": "was", "s": 102.4, "e": 102.64}, {"w": "windy.", "s": 102.64, "e": 103.0}]}, {"start": 105.86, "end": 110.36, "text": "He seems to be ill. It seems that he is ill.", "words": [{"w": "He", "s": 105.86, "e": 106.58}, {"w": "seems", "s": 106.58, "e": 107.02}, {"w": "to", "s": 107.02, "e": 107.26}, {"w": "be", "s": 107.26, "e": 107.44}, {"w": "ill.", "s": 107.44, "e": 107.74}, {"w": "It", "s": 108.72, "e": 108.94}, {"w": "seems", "s": 108.94, "e": 109.36}, {"w": "that", "s": 109.36, "e": 109.64}, {"w": "he", "s": 109.64, "e": 109.84}, {"w": "is", "s": 109.84, "e": 110.02}, {"w": "ill.", "s": 110.02, "e": 110.36}]}, {"start": 113.62, "end": 115.56, "text": "You worry about it too much.", "words": [{"w": "You", "s": 113.62, "e": 113.94}, {"w": "worry", "s": 113.94, "e": 114.34}, {"w": "about", "s": 114.34, "e": 114.7}, {"w": "it", "s": 114.7, "e": 114.92}, {"w": "too", "s": 114.92, "e": 115.18}, {"w": "much.", "s": 115.18, "e": 115.56}]}, {"start": 118.54, "end": 120.28, "text": "What is worrying you?", "words": [{"w": "What", "s": 118.54, "e": 119.26}, {"w": "is", "s": 119.26, "e": 119.48}, {"w": "worrying", "s": 119.48, "e": 119.88}, {"w": "you?", "s": 119.88, "e": 120.28}]}, {"start": 123.08, "end": 126.18, "text": "Thank you for your concern about my health.", "words": [{"w": "Thank", "s": 123.08, "e": 123.82}, {"w": "you", "s": 123.82, "e": 124.12}, {"w": "for", "s": 124.12, "e": 124.34}, {"w": "your", "s": 124.34, "e": 124.54}, {"w": "concern", "s": 124.54, "e": 125.08}, {"w": "about", "s": 125.08, "e": 125.36}, {"w": "my", "s": 125.36, "e": 125.64}, {"w": "health.", "s": 125.64, "e": 126.18}]}, {"start": 129.14, "end": 131.74, "text": "Jim is anxious about his health.", "words": [{"w": "Jim", "s": 129.14, "e": 129.88}, {"w": "is", "s": 129.88, "e": 130.14}, {"w": "anxious", "s": 130.14, "e": 130.54}, {"w": "about", "s": 130.54, "e": 130.94}, {"w": "his", "s": 130.94, "e": 131.22}, {"w": "health.", "s": 131.22, "e": 131.74}]}, {"start": 134.68, "end": 137.5, "text": "She was anxious to know the results.", "words": [{"w": "She", "s": 134.68, "e": 135.42}, {"w": "was", "s": 135.42, "e": 135.62}, {"w": "anxious", "s": 135.62, "e": 136.1}, {"w": "to", "s": 136.1, "e": 136.5}, {"w": "know", "s": 136.5, "e": 136.74}, {"w": "the", "s": 136.74, "e": 136.92}, {"w": "results.", "s": 136.92, "e": 137.5}]}, {"start": 140.54, "end": 144.24, "text": "The music from the next room is starting to annoy me.", "words": [{"w": "The", "s": 140.54, "e": 141.14}, {"w": "music", "s": 141.14, "e": 141.5}, {"w": "from", "s": 141.5, "e": 141.8}, {"w": "the", "s": 141.8, "e": 141.98}, {"w": "next", "s": 141.98, "e": 142.24}, {"w": "room", "s": 142.24, "e": 142.62}, {"w": "is", "s": 142.62, "e": 142.88}, {"w": "starting", "s": 142.88, "e": 143.28}, {"w": "to", "s": 143.28, "e": 143.62}, {"w": "annoy", "s": 143.62, "e": 143.96}, {"w": "me.", "s": 143.96, "e": 144.24}]}, {"start": 147.24, "end": 150.64, "text": "I'm feeling nervous about the interview on Friday.", "words": [{"w": "I'm", "s": 147.24, "e": 147.96}, {"w": "feeling", "s": 147.96, "e": 148.36}, {"w": "nervous", "s": 148.36, "e": 148.84}, {"w": "about", "s": 148.84, "e": 149.2}, {"w": "the", "s": 149.2, "e": 149.44}, {"w": "interview", "s": 149.44, "e": 149.94}, {"w": "on", "s": 149.94, "e": 150.22}, {"w": "Friday.", "s": 150.22, "e": 150.64}]}, {"start": 153.64, "end": 156.92, "text": "She was really upset when she heard the news.", "words": [{"w": "She", "s": 153.64, "e": 154.36}, {"w": "was", "s": 154.36, "e": 154.6}, {"w": "really", "s": 154.6, "e": 154.98}, {"w": "upset", "s": 154.98, "e": 155.5}, {"w": "when", "s": 155.5, "e": 155.84}, {"w": "she", "s": 155.84, "e": 156.08}, {"w": "heard", "s": 156.08, "e": 156.38}, {"w": "the", "s": 156.38, "e": 156.54}, {"w": "news.", "s": 156.54, "e": 156.92}]}, {"start": 160.22, "end": 162.68, "text": "Does the sound of the TV bother you?", "words": [{"w": "Does", "s": 160.22, "e": 160.56}, {"w": "the", "s": 160.56, "e": 160.8}, {"w": "sound", "s": 160.8, "e": 161.14}, {"w": "of", "s": 161.14, "e": 161.34}, {"w": "the", "s": 161.34, "e": 161.5}, {"w": "TV", "s": 161.5, "e": 161.86}, {"w": "bother", "s": 161.86, "e": 162.36}, {"w": "you?", "s": 162.36, "e": 162.68}]}, {"start": 165.62, "end": 169.58, "text": "Many of these diseases are thought to be caused by stress.", "words": [{"w": "Many", "s": 165.62, "e": 166.34}, {"w": "of", "s": 166.34, "e": 166.6}, {"w": "these", "s": 166.6, "e": 166.82}, {"w": "diseases", "s": 166.82, "e": 167.44}, {"w": "are", "s": 167.44, "e": 167.8}, {"w": "thought", "s": 167.8, "e": 168.1}, {"w": "to", "s": 168.1, "e": 168.32}, {"w": "be", "s": 168.32, "e": 168.46}, {"w": "caused", "s": 168.46, "e": 168.88}, {"w": "by", "s": 168.88, "e": 169.16}, {"w": "stress.", "s": 169.16, "e": 169.58}]}, {"start": 172.32, "end": 174.64, "text": "He stressed this point.", "words": [{"w